<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>With 85 years of experience in 91 leading <a data-udi="umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d}" title="Ski Resorts">ski resorts</a> across 9 countries in Europe Canada &amp; Japan, Inghams offers all the choice you need for your winter 2019/20 ski holiday. Whether you are a first-time skier, you’re returning after a brief hiatus or you are an advanced skier looking for the latest challenge, we offer resorts to suit every ability. And if you’re looking to accommodate a mixed ability group, we have that covered too - take a look at our Insider’s Guides for inspiration and advice on the best resorts for you! <br /><br />You’ll also discover plenty of choice when it comes to your accommodation - from <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/accommodation-options/apartment" title="apartments">self-catering apartments</a> and partner hotels to <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/accommodation-options/chalet" title="chalet">catered chalets</a> and <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/accommodation-options/chalet-hotel" title="CH2">Chalet Hotels</a> with friendly Inghams staff to take care of you. <br /><br />Still can’t decide? Get in touch on <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.facebook.com/inghamsSki/" target="_blank">Facebook</a> or <a rel="noopener" href="https://twitter.com/InghamsSki" target="_blank">Twitter</a>, or give our friendly reservations agents a call on 01483 938 385 – if you’re looking for first-hand experience of our resorts then these are the team for you!</p>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 20px; width: 170px;">
