<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Meet our experts and read our Insider's Guides!</h2>
<br />
<p>Inghams have been taking our guests to the mountains for 85 years – we are the ski &amp; snowboard experts and we know how to build the perfect ski trip for our guests’ requirements. We have a large team of knowledgeable and experienced skiers and snowboarders both in the UK and overseas, who are passionate about making sure you have a great, well-deserved holiday from the minute you enquire, right through to the time you get home.<br /><br />We've assembled this wide base of knowledge into a collection of fun and informative <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/articles/winter-insiders-guides" title="IGs">Insider's Guides</a>, to assist you when it comes to trying to unearth where is best for beginner skiers, or where might have the best après ski bars. You can also <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BB4gzEXbZ0g&amp;list=PLWrXDQnZTbN-IrVh8PzZIZZbdt0Pj8KDd" target="_blank">meet our Product Managers</a> and hear what they have to say about their favourite ski resorts. <br /><br /></p>
<div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UnVe9dtd8A8?list=PLWrXDQnZTbN-IrVh8PzZIZZbdt0Pj8KDd" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h1>Check out our helpful holiday advice sections!</h1>
<br />
<p>It always tough to know where to start when it comes to picking your ski holiday. Where's best to take a group or a family? And which chalet suits your party best? With that in mind we've put together some helpful advice sections, helping you to find out what might be best for your holiday this year, scroll on to find these useful tips.</p>
</div>
